Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready! {/lets go}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep shooting! Barrage fire! \NMore torpedo bombers incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn thing...
